PACKAGE DEPENDANCIES: Python 2.X, Pygame (both should be available through your package manager)

w / up = up one half tile
s / down = down one half tile
a / left = left one half tile
d / right = right one half tile

x = next tile
z = previous tile
t = go up one layer
y = go down one layer

enter = place tile
backspace = delete tile

c = toggle collidable on map tile (not the tile tied to the cursor)
m = print map to file

escape = quit
